For past few months, I have been working on some useful utilities like the editor utilities and other stuffs like that. I have introduced an editor utility which can be used to deploy component on multiple gameObjects at the same time.\
\
\
In this version I have introduced a simpler way to implement theme level box you might have seen in various games. Like you have a set of several levels and you want to put each one of them inside a main level box like Angry Birds has.\
\
Now I have tried to make it more easier and customizable by exposing some useful properties like scale down, movement, speed, etc.\
\
\
